---
// No special Astro script needed
---

<style>
    .faq-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }
  
    .faq {
      background-color: #1e1e1e;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
  
    .faq-question {
      background-color: #1e1e1e;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
  
    .faq-question:hover {
      background-color: #2a2a2a;
    }
  
    .faq-answer {
      background-color: #252525;
      color: #dcdcdc;
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.3s ease, padding 0.3s ease;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  
    .faq.open .faq-answer {
      max-height: 200px;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  
    .faq-icon {
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
  
    .faq.open .faq-icon {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }
  
    /* Optional: Adjust spacing and shadow for a sleek card effect */
    .faq {
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .faq-header {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif; /* Example font, change as desired */
    font-size: 2rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-description {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  </style>
  
  <div class="faq-container">
    <h2 class="faq-header">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <p class="faq-description">
        Here are some common questions and answers to help you get the most out of AI365. If you need more assistance, feel free to reach out!
    </p>

    <div class="faq">
      <div class="faq-question">
        Are there any subscription fees or after-purchase payments?
        <span class="faq-icon">➤</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        No, AI365 does not have any subscription fees or additional costs after purchase.
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="faq">
      <div class="faq-question">
        What is the battery life of AI365?
        <span class="faq-icon">➤</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        The battery life lasts up to 12 hours on a full charge with typical use.
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="faq">
      <div class="faq-question">
        Is there an app for parents to check usage on their phones?
        <span class="faq-icon">➤</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Yes, there is a companion app available for both iOS and Android.
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="faq">
      <div class="faq-question">
        Does AI365 come with a SIM card for data?
        <span class="faq-icon">➤</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Yes, AI365 includes a pre-installed SIM card for easy setup.
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="faq">
      <div class="faq-question">
        How is content saved?
        <span class="faq-icon">➤</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        Content is saved securely to the cloud, accessible from your account at any time.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      const faqs = document.querySelectorAll('.faq');
  
      faqs.forEach(faq => {
        faq.querySelector('.faq-question').addEventListener('click', () => {
          faq.classList.toggle('open');
        });
      });
    });
  </script>
  